<section class="hero" aria-label="ヒーロー">
  <div class="hero-bg-char" aria-hidden="true">戦</div>

  <div class="hero-inner container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-line"></span>
        SENGOKU × MODERN STRATEGY
      </p>

      <h1 class="hero-title">
        戦国武将の判断が、<br>
        <em>あなたの正解</em>になる。
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-body">
        命がかかった合戦室で磨かれた戦略は、<br class="br-pc">
        現代の会議・交渉・組織にそのまま使える。<br class="br-pc">
        500年前の知恵を、今日の武器に変える。
      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/blog/" class="cta-primary">記事を読む →</a>
        <a href="/books/" class="cta-secondary">おすすめ書籍</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-numbers" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-num">
        <span class="num-val">01</span>
        <span class="num-label">合戦×ビジネス</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-num">
        <span class="num-val">02</span>
        <span class="num-label">武将×リーダーシップ</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-num">
        <span class="num-val">03</span>
        <span class="num-label">兵法×現代戦略</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--bg-navy);
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg-char {
    position: absolute;
    right: -2rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(16rem, 35vw, 32rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.07);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 4rem;
    padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 4rem);
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.4rem;
    max-width: 660px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--orange);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .eyebrow-line {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--orange);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.5vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--orange);
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-title em::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0.05em;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 0.06em;
    background: var(--orange);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 2.1;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.5);
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2.4rem;
    background: var(--orange);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: var(--orange-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .cta-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--orange);
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  /* 右サイドの番号リスト */
  .hero-numbers {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-num {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.3);
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .num-val {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.5);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .num-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { min-height: auto; }
    .hero-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 3rem;
      padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 3rem);
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .hero-numbers {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-inner {
      padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 2rem);
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .hero-numbers { gap: 1.2rem; }
    .num-val { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .br-pc { display: none; }
  }
</style>
